steroids last night, and within a few hours, much of the pain had subsided.
He hasn't needed morphine all day.

He is in good spirits, all things considered.  For example, I asked how he
was doing and he said "Terrible!  All three of my fantasy football teams
lost, and I've got a tumor exploding in my head!"  He's being moved into
private room today, so personal visits, flowers, and phone calls will be
welcome.  The main number is 210-575-4040.  Just ask for Ernst.

